<p source="SHANGBO.XIANGBANGZHIDAO 4.20.1 (STRIP 1) JI XUSHENG 4: 126"><pb xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-1a.1">先其欲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-1a.2">服其強,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-1a.3">牧其患</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-1a.4">靜以待,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-1a.5">待時出</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-1a.6">故此事事出政,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-1a.7">政毋忘所治事 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.XIANGBANGZHIDAO 4.20.2 (STRIP 1) JI XUSHENG 4: 126"><pb xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-2a.1">[...] 人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-2a.2">可謂相邦矣</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-2a.3">公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-2a.4">敢問民事?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-2a.5">[...] 孔子</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.XIANGBANGZHIDAO 4.20.3 (STRIP 2) JI XUSHENG 4: 126"><pb xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-3a.1">[...] 農夫勸於耕,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-3a.2">以實官倉</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-3a.3">百工勸於事,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-3a.4">以實府庫</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-3a.5">庶民勸於四肢之藝,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-3a.6">以備軍旅 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.XIANGBANGZHIDAO 4.20.4 (STRIP 3) JI XUSHENG 4: 126"><pb xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.1">[...]者</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.2">孔子退,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.3">告子貢曰</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.4">吾見於君,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.5">不問有邦之道</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.6">而問相邦之道</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.7">不亦愆乎</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.8">子貢曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.9">吾子之答也何如?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.10">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0049_tls_001-4a.11">汝思</seg></p>

</div>
